# Project Setup

**pnpm workspace monorepo** (pnpm@10.17.1)

## Apps
- `apps/presentation` - Next.js app (port 3000, default)
- `apps/user-testing` - Next.js app (port 3001)

## Commands

### Root level (targets presentation by default)
```bash
pnpm dev        # Run presentation dev server
pnpm build      # Build presentation
pnpm start      # Start presentation prod server
pnpm lint       # Lint presentation
```

### Specific app
```bash
pnpm --filter presentation dev    # Port 3000
pnpm --filter user-testing dev    # Port 3001
pnpm --filter <app-name> <command>
```

### All apps
```bash
pnpm -r dev     # Run dev in all apps
pnpm -r build   # Build all apps
```

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router, Turbopack)
- React 19
- TypeScript 5
- Tailwind CSS 4
- ESLint 9


